    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AcousticGrandPianoStrategy
    Strategy implementation for the Acoustic Grand Piano instrument.
    ElectricBassGuitarStrategy
    Strategy implementation for the Electric Bass Guitar instrument.
    HigherPitchStrategy
    Strategy implementation that raises the pitch of notes.
    InstrumentStrategy
    Strategy interface for applying different instruments to a MIDI track.
    LegatoMidiEventFactory
    Legato implementation of the MidiEventFactory interface.
    LegatoMidiEventFactoryAbstract
    Abstract factory implementation that creates LegatoMidiEventFactory instances.
    LowerPitchStrategy
    Strategy implementation that lowers the pitch of notes.
    Main
    Main application class for MyLittleMozart.
    MidiCsvParser
    Utility class for parsing MIDI data from CSV files.
    MidiEventData
    Data class that stores MIDI event information parsed from CSV files.
    MidiEventFactory
    Interface for creating MIDI events using the Factory pattern.
    MidiEventFactoryAbstract
    Abstract Factory interface for creating different types of MidiEventFactory instances.
    PitchStrategy
    Strategy interface for modifying the pitch of MIDI notes.
    StaccatoMidiEventFactory
    Staccato implementation of the MidiEventFactory interface.
    StaccatoMidiEventFactoryAbstract
    Abstract factory implementation that creates StaccatoMidiEventFactory instances.
    StandardMidiEventFactory
    Standard implementation of the MidiEventFactory interface.
    StandardMidiEventFactoryAbstract
    Abstract factory implementation that creates StandardMidiEventFactory instances.
    TrumpetStrategy
    Strategy implementation for the Trumpet instrument.
